    "is_free": false,
    "description": "《僭越：无光之日》将带领玩家以第一人称视角经历一场充满悬疑与恐怖的冒险，玩家会深入与世隔绝的云林村，直面那些隐藏于黑暗当中的罪恶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/6ce3ac767973d1aaf8104708fbd873fe.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br>在这个被黑暗笼罩的村落中，潜伏着众多不可名状的怪物，它们既有着惊悚的外表，也有着惨痛的过去。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/4fdf981b89c30026015489d4d97249ee.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/4fdf981b89c30026015489d4d97249ee.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/4fdf981b89c30026015489d4d97249ee.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f8b86c3ac2a645edae66deb3d53cb4f6.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br>云林村的过去有着太多有待探寻的真相，那些奇怪的习俗，神秘的仪式，不明所以的机关，都在揭示着一场迫在眉睫的危机！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/8947d8128d01104038c9a89ad3def189.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/8947d8128d01104038c9a89ad3def189.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/8947d8128d01104038c9a89ad3def189.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/050657187b58befaf96389e1063c3515.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/050657187b58befaf96389e1063c3515.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/050657187b58befaf96389e1063c3515.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/afecb272c8382fdb9eac106ef133e822.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br>身处阴云密布、危机四伏的村落当中，你必须借助一切可能的手段，小心探索，才有可能逃出生天。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/0c59402096906a73263928c7a69e56b6.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/0c59402096906a73263928c7a69e56b6.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/0c59402096906a73263928c7a69e56b6.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/6cc3d7d290811adaf70f95a6374c7ae5.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/6cc3d7d290811adaf70f95a6374c7ae5.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/6cc3d7d290811adaf70f95a6374c7ae5.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/48eed0f03756629c36051cc5db1eaeef.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br>风格多样的机关谜题遍布地图，声音、光线、垃圾乃至恐怖的怪物都可能是关键线索，直面恐惧，找出破解之道吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f6d2194a9d0ceaca983de5655954704a.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f6d2194a9d0ceaca983de5655954704a.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f6d2194a9d0ceaca983de5655954704a.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/b5f4b2fb3440f7d23faf5515be88db6a.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br>从远古的神迹，到二战侵华日军的暴行，再到后来神鬼莫测的邪教，为什么这个小小的山村会陷入无尽的恐惧？一切的答案尽在这场恐怖盛焰当中！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/78ee499572df5cf2d5e42e7f879b5d91.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/78ee499572df5cf2d5e42e7f879b5d91.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/78ee499572df5cf2d5e42e7f879b5d91.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
